# Per-version download breakdown (choose one):

# Option 1: BigQuery (recommended, free 1TB/month)
# Set up a Google Cloud service account with BigQuery access
# Either set the path to the JSON key file:
# GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=/path/to/service-account-key.json
# Or paste the JSON content directly:
# BIGQUERY_CREDENTIALS={"type":"service_account","project_id":"...","private_key":"..."}

# Option 2: Pepy.tech API (alternative, requires Pro plan $8/mo)
# PEPY_API_KEY=your_key_here
